      <h1>Secure Funding</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Find resources and grants to fund your team's operations.</p>
      <section class="content-section">
        <p>Funding usually covers registration fees, parts, tools, travel, and event costs. Start with a simple budget so you know how much money the team actually needs.</p>
        <div class="content-subsection">
          <h3>Common funding sources</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>School activity funds or club budgets</li>
            <li>Local businesses willing to sponsor STEM programs</li>
            <li>Community grants, booster clubs, or PTA groups</li>
            <li>Small fundraisers like demo nights or donation drives</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Action:</strong> Make a one-page sponsor sheet that explains the team, the budget, and what sponsors get in return.</p>
